474
00:29:27,493 --> 00:29:28,753
Kau kan bukan amatiran.

475
00:29:29,524 --> 00:29:32,193
Bagaimana denganmu? Kenapa kau bertanya?

476
00:29:34,663 --> 00:29:35,764
Hanya...

477
00:29:36,733 --> 00:29:38,503
