542
00:35:59,514 --> 00:36:02,014
Kau tampak kalem, tapi sebenarnya kau benar-benar berjiwa bebas.

543
00:36:03,514 --> 00:36:04,653
Baiklah.

544
00:36:04,983 --> 00:36:06,324
Jika kau menjawab pertanyaanku,

545
00:36:06,554 --> 00:36:08,653
