546
00:36:08,954 --> 00:36:10,594
Kau bilang tergila-gila padaku.

547
00:36:10,594 --> 00:36:11,963
Semua itu masa lalu.

548
00:36:11,963 --> 00:36:14,034
Aku sedang bekerja sekarang, jadi aku sibuk.

549
00:36:14,034 --> 00:36:15,264
Sudah dulu, ya.

550
00:36:21,403 --> 00:36:24,673
